{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, if the chatbot has enough preliminary information, it could create humanlike dialogues not only from the perspective of similarity to human language but also considering the meaning of the lines, adding some notes of humor, skepticism, and even flirting, according to the genre.",
    "The more details are generated from the previous steps, the easier it will be for the chatbot to create truthful dialogues that have an emotional and psychological impact on the reader.",
    "We also noticed that creativeness in dialogue generation depends on the genre: if the story is more adventurous, the lines will be written in a general way.",
    "However, ChatGPT appeared to write quite interesting and human-like dialogues in the detective genre (Figure 4).",
    "The generated descriptions can be presented in the form of a complex text, as well as divided into semantic parts, depending on what is being described."
  ]
}